OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FKurdish-Iranian dissident groups based
OL,7,Fin northern Iraq have said they are
OL,8,Fpreparing for a potential cross-border
OL,9,Fmilitary operation in Iran, and the US
OL,10,Fhas reportedly asked Iraqi Kurds to
OL,11,Fsupport them.
OL,13,FThe Kurdish groups are widely seen as
OL,14,Fthe most well-organised segment of the
OL,15,Ffragmented Iranian opposition and are
OL,16,Fbelieved to have thousands of trained
OL,17,Ffighters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
