OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772831515
OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FTheir entry into the war could pose a
OL,7,Fsignificant challenge to the embattled
OL,8,Fauthorities in Tehran and could also
OL,9,Frisk pulling Iraq further into the
OL,10,Fconflict.
OL,12,FITV News understands that since last
OL,13,Fyear, weapons have been smuggled into
OL,14,FWestern Iran to arm thousands of
OL,15,FKurdish volunteers. They are expected
OL,16,Fto begin a ground operation within
OL,17,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
