CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772831515
OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FIn recent days, American and Israeli
OL,7,Fstrikes have repeatedly struck
OL,8,Fsecurity targets in the West of the
OL,9,Fcountry to degrade their capabilities
OL,10,Fand give the best chance for the
OL,11,Fground rebellion.
OL,13,FITV News has been told by Kurdish
OL,14,Fsources that American and Israeli
OL,15,Fforces have been asked to provide air
OL,16,Fcover when any such ground operation
OL,17,Fbegins. Our sources do not know if
OL,18,Fthat request has been approved.
OL,20,FWho are the Kurds?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
