OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FThe Kurds are an ethnic group residing
OL,7,Fprimarily in Iran, Iraq, Syria and
OL,8,FTurkey.
OL,10,FIt is believed they number around 40
OL,11,Fmillion, and many consider them to be
OL,12,Fthe largest distinct ethnic population
OL,13,Fto not have its own state - something
OL,14,Fthey have sought for decades,
OL,15,Falongside greater autonomy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
