PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772831515
OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FIf the Iranian and Iraqi Kurdish
OL,7,Fgroups were to join the war, it would
OL,8,Fbe the first entry of a significant
OL,9,Fground force into the battle. The
OL,10,FKurdish groups have battle experience
OL,11,Ffrom their fight against the Islamic
OL,12,FState group.
OL,14,FAn official with Komala, another of
OL,15,Fthe Kurdish Iranian groups, said
OL,16,FWednesday that their forces are ready
OL,17,Fto cross the border within a week to
OL,18,Ften days and were "waiting for the
OL,19,Fgrounds to be suitable."
OL,26,@zD@SOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
