OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FHe spoke on condition of anonymity out
OL,7,Fof security concerns.
OL,9,FKurds in Iran have a long history of
OL,10,Fgrievances and uprisings against both
OL,11,Fthe current Islamic Republic and the
OL,12,Fmonarchy that preceded it. During the
OL,13,Frule of Shah Mohammad Reza Pahlavi,
OL,14,FKurds were marginalized and repressed,
OL,15,Fand sometimes rebelled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
