OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FThe death of Mahsa Amini
OL,8,FKurdish groups have been at the
OL,9,Fforefront of previous clashes with the
OL,10,FIranian regime.
OL,12,FIn 2022, a 22-year-old Kurdish woman,
OL,13,FMahsa Amini, died in custody after
OL,14,Fbeing arrested by Iran's morality
OL,15,Fpolice for allegedly breaking the
OL,16,Fcountry's strict dress code for women.
OL,18,FHer death led to national protests at
OL,19,Fwhich Kurdish groups were integral,
OL,20,Fand brought Kurdish concerns over
OL,21,Findependence to the fore.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
