CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772831515
OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FThe protests were eventually shut down
OL,7,Fby the Iranian regime, with territory
OL,8,Fclaimed by the Kurds retaken.
OL,10,FWill the Kurds take arms against Iran?
OL,12,FAmid escalating attacks on Iran,
OL,13,Fseveral officials claimed that US
OL,14,FPresident Donald Trump has spoken with
OL,15,Fthe heads of Kurdish groups in the
OL,16,Fregion to discuss the situation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772831515
OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FOne of the officials said Trump had
OL,7,Fasked the Iraqi Kurds to militarily
OL,8,Fsupport the Iranian Kurdish groups in
OL,9,Foperations in Iran, and to open the
OL,10,Fborder to allow the Iranian Kurdish
OL,11,Fgroups to move freely back and forth.
OL,13,FWhen asked about the call and reports
OL,14,Fthat Trump has sought military support
OL,15,Ffor Iranian Kurdish groups, White
OL,16,FHouse press secretary Karoline Leavitt
OL,17,Fsaid: "He did speak to Kurdish leaders
OL,18,Fwith respect to our base that we have
OL,19,Fin northern Iraq," but denied that
OL,20,FTrump had agreed to a specific plan.
OL,26,@yD@GOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
