OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772831515
OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FThe Iraqi Kurdish official said the
OL,7,FIraqi Kurds were concerned that
OL,8,Fgetting directly involved in the
OL,9,Fconflict would draw a harsh Iranian
OL,10,Fresponse.
OL,12,FAlready, the Kurdish region has seen a
OL,13,Fstring of drone and missile attacks by
OL,14,FIran and allied Iraqi militias in
OL,15,Frecent days, targeting US military
OL,16,Fbases and the US Consulate in Irbil as
OL,17,Fwell as the Kurdish groups' bases.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
