PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772831515
OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FWhile most of the attacks have been
OL,7,Fintercepted, civilian homes have been
OL,8,Fdamaged, and the region is suffering
OL,9,Ffrom electricity cuts after a key gas
OL,10,Ffield halted operations due to
OL,11,Fsecurity concerns.
OL,13,FIn a statement, the PUK - the Kurdish
OL,14,Fpolitical party in Iraq - confirmed
OL,15,Fthat their leader had spoken by phone
OL,16,Fwith Trump, who "provided
OL,17,Fclarification and vision regarding US
OL,18,Fobjectives in the war."
OL,26,@xD@QOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
