OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FThe statement said the PUK "believes
OL,7,Fthat the best solution is a return to
OL,8,Fthe negotiating table."
OL,10,FSpokespeople for the Kurdish regional
OL,11,Fgovernment in Iraq declined to comment.
OL,26,@nD@\OUpD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
