OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FAsked about reports that the Trump
OL,7,Fadministration was considering arming
OL,8,FIranian Kurdish groups, Defence
OL,9,FSecretary Pete Hegseth told reporters
OL,10,FWednesday: "None of our objectives are
OL,11,Fpremised on the support or the arming
OL,12,Fof any particular force. So, what
OL,13,Fother entities may be doing, we're
OL,14,Faware of, but our objectives aren't
OL,15,Fcentered on that."
OL,17,FWhat are the drawbacks for Kurdish
OL,18,Fforces getting involved?
OL,26,@rD@LOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
