OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIraq's National Security Adviser
OL,12,FQassim al-Araji said in a post on X
OL,13,Fthat Ali Bagheri, deputy secretary of
OL,14,FIran's Supreme National Security
OL,15,FCouncil, had requested in a call
OL,16,Fbetween them "that Iraq take the
OL,17,Fnecessary measures to prevent any
OL,18,Fopposition groups from infiltrating
OL,19,Fthe border between the two countries."
OL,26,@xD@NOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
