OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772831515
OL,3,CWho are the Kurds, and could they
OL,4,Ctopple the Iranian regime?
OL,6,FAl-Araji said Iraq is committed to
OL,7,F"preventing any groups from
OL,8,Finfiltrating or crossing the Iranian
OL,9,Fborder or carrying out terrorist acts
OL,10,Ffrom Iraqi territory" and noted that
OL,11,Fsecurity reinforcements had been sent
OL,12,Fto the border.
OL,14,FIn addition to retaliation by Iran,
OL,15,Fany movement by Iraqi Kurds to join a
OL,16,Fcross-border attack would likely
OL,17,Finflame tensions with Iran-backed
OL,18,FIraqi militias, which have already
OL,19,Fclaimed missile and drone strikes on
OL,20,FIrbil in recent days.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/18
